songs.title: Fly Away (Snippet)
songs.lyrics:
Fly away
I've missed you when I tried to say
I had to fly away
But I'll be over you some day
Fly away
I've missed you when I tried to say
I had to fly away
But I'll be over you some day

[Instrumental]

(Yeah, yeah)
I guess we back again
Everybody just vibe in there
Mmm, I guess we back again
Everybody just vibe in there
